    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Upon reaching 17th level, you have become adept at laying ambushes and quickly escaping danger. You can now take a second Bonus Action on your turn, provided it is a Bonus Action from your Cunning Action.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of once), and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p><p>When you take damage you can reduce the damage you take by half. You can do this once per turn.</p><p>You cannot reduce damage taken in this way if you are incapacitated or your movement speed is 0 before.</p>",
